card.name: User story for showing worker availability
card.desc:
As a business owner, I want to view worker availability so that I can schedule working times for my employees.
I need to be able to see each worker's timetable simultaneously so that I can allocate all of my employees shifts without clashes.

card.name: User story for looking at booking summaries
card.desc:
As a business owner, I want to view booking summaries so that I can organize and keep track of customer bookings.
I need to be able to see details for bookings in chronological order so that I can plan out bookings ahead of time in order of increasing priority.

cards.desc:
As a business owner, I want to view booking summaries so that I can organize and keep track of customer bookings.
I need to be able to see details for bookings in chronological order so that I can plan out bookings ahead of time in order of increasing priority.
cards.name: User story for looking at booking summaries

cards.desc:
As a business owner, I want to view worker availability so that I can schedule working times for my employees.
I need to be able to see each worker's timetable simultaneously so that I can allocate all of my employees shifts without clashes.
